12
00:02:39,000 --> 00:02:39,320
Pero...

13
00:02:39,320 --> 00:02:42,140
...es tu último recurso,
 de un solo uso.

14
00:02:42,140 --> 00:02:44,210
¡Si fallas, es tu fin!

15
00:03:43,600 --> 00:03:45,070
